<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Mishwa Birthday Scrapbook 🎉</title>
<style>
body{
  margin:0;
  font-family: "Comic Sans MS", cursive;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg,#ff9a9e,#fbc2eb,#a6c1ee);
  color:white;
  overflow:hidden;
  text-align:center;
}
.page{
  display:none;
  padding:40px;
  min-height:100vh;
  position:relative;
  border-radius:20px;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  box-shadow:0 10px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}
.page.active{
  display:block;
  animation:fade 1s;
}
@keyframes fade{
  0%{opacity:0; transform:scale(0.9);}
  100%{opacity:1; transform:scale(1);}
}
h1{
  font-size:38px;
  margin-bottom:10px;
  text-shadow: 2px 2px 5px #ff69b4;
}
p{
  font-size:20px;
  line-height:1.6em;
  max-width:750px;
  margin:auto;
}
button{
  margin-top:30px;
  padding:12px 30px;
  font-size:18px;
  border:none;
  border-radius:20px;
  background:white;
  color:#ff4fa3;
  cursor:pointer;
  transition:0.3s;
}
button:hover{
  transform:scale(1.1);
}
.sticker{
  display:inline-block;
  font-size:40px;
  margin:10px;
  animation:pop 0.8s ease;
}
@keyframes pop{
  0%{transform:scale(0);}
  50%{transform:scale(1.3);}
  100%{transform:scale(1);}
}
.sparkle{
  position:absolute;
  animation:float 6s linear infinite;
  font-size:20px;
}
@keyframes float{
  0%{transform:translateY(100vh);}
  100%{transform:translateY(-20vh);}
}
@keyframes confetti-fall{
  0% {transform: translateY(0) rotate(0deg);}
  100% {transform: translateY(100vh) rotate(360deg);}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Pages 1 to 6 -->

<div class="page active" id="p1">
<h1>🎁 Surprise for Mishwa 🎁</h1>
<p>Hey Mishwa! 🌸💖  
This scrapbook is packed with our memories, gossip, jokes, and chaotic adventures 😎✨  
Since Grade 7, every day has been unforgettable 🏫💫  
Boring classes became fun, small incidents became epic stories 😂🌈</p>
<div>
<span class="sticker">🌸</span>
<span class="sticker">💖</span>
<span class="sticker">✨</span>
</div>
<button onclick="nextPage()">Open 📖</button>
</div>

<div class="page" id="p2">
<h1>📚 Grade 7 → Grade 8 Memories</h1>
<p>Lunch break gossip 🥪💬, secret commentary 🤫, and random class moments turned epic 💫  
Copying funny teacher mistakes, exchanging smiles, and jokes 👀💖  
Even boring lectures became memorable 🌈✨</p>
<div>
<span class="sticker">😂</span>
<span class="sticker">💫</span>
<span class="sticker">💖</span>
</div>
<button onclick="nextPage()">Next ➡️</button>
</div>

<div class="page" id="p3">
<h1>👑 Certified Hong Kong Baddie 👑</h1>
<p>Mishwa, you are the ultimate baddie 😎💅  
Energy: 1000% ⚡ Chaos: 1000% 🌪  
Secret smiles, pranks, and fun make every day memorable 💖  
Even boring lectures turn into adventures 🌸✨  
Inside jokes that nobody else gets 🤣💫</p>
<div>
<span class="sticker">🔥</span>
<span class="sticker">🌸</span>
<span class="sticker">💖</span>
</div>
<button onclick="nextPage()">Next ➡️</button>
</div>

<div class="page" id="p4">
<h1>🕵️ Gossip & Chaos 🕵️‍♀️</h1>
<p>We are the class reporters 📢😆  
Code names for everyone 🤫  
Whisper commentary 💬  
Small things → huge drama 🎭💥  
Copying teachers, laughing at mistakes 😂  
Our secret world of chaos ✨💖🌈</p>
<div>
<span class="sticker">💬</span>
<span class="sticker">🤫</span>
<span class="sticker">😂</span>
</div>
<button onclick="nextPage()">Next ➡️</button>
</div>

<div class="page" id="p5">
<h1>😂 Inside Jokes & Daily Chaos 😝</h1>
<p>Random looks 👀, silent laughter 🤫, memes in seconds 🤣  
Doing masti, bunking, going late to class, making excuses 😎💥  
Chaos & fun that’s 100% ours 🌈💖✨  
Every day is an adventure 🎉</p>
<div>
<span class="sticker">🤣</span>
<span class="sticker">🌸</span>
<span class="sticker">💖</span>
</div>
